<instructionalPlan>CS4 plan: |n - Introduce the topic by explaining that you sometimes may find yourself working with a damaged image and want to repair it, or that you may wish to cover other types of "blemishes in a picture", and that Photoshop comes with a set of tools for this: Clone stamp, Spot healing brush, Healing brush, and Patch tool |n The explain and demo how to use the clone stamp tool |n  |n PRACTICE: Scenario based multiple choice on using the clone stamp tool</instructionalPlan>
